Package: pdfoxide
Type: Package
Title: Fast PDF Text, Markdown and HTML Extraction (pdf_oxide)
Version: 0.3.74
Authors@R: person("Yury", "Fedoseev", email = "yfedoseev@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Yury Fedoseev [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Yury Fedoseev <yfedoseev@gmail.com>
Description: The fastest PDF library for R: 0.8ms mean, 5x faster than the
    industry leaders, 100% pass rate on 3,830 real-world PDFs. Idiomatic R
    bindings for fast extraction of reading-order text, Markdown and HTML from
    PDF documents, plus building PDFs from Markdown, HTML or text. Wraps the
    pdf_oxide Rust core via its C ABI.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/yfedoseev/pdf_oxide
Encoding: UTF-8
Suggests: tinytest
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
